## Interface: 20505
## Title: Super Swing Timer
## Notes: Melee and ranged swing timer for Classic and TBC. Includes Blizzard options panel support, class-colored swing bars with opacity-aware color swatches, in-addon texture previews, a latency-aware hunter Auto Shot cooldown line, a dedicated Hunter Auto Shot / Multi-Shot cast bar, adjustable bar border size, dedicated spark and weave texture browsers, bar-only texture filtering, a UnitAura-aware paladin seal breakpoint line, a temporary Test Bars preview for moving frames, and color-coded shaman weave assist overlays with per-family toggles that stay above the bar fill.
